729
00:35:49,392 --> 00:35:50,658
Dia akan baik-baik saja?

730
00:35:50,660 --> 00:35:52,793
Apa tadi kau melihat pria
kearah sini?

731
00:35:52,795 --> 00:35:55,629
Tinggi, bersetelan bagus?

732
00:35:55,631 --> 00:35:56,864
Ya.

733
00:35:56,866 --> 00:35:58,499
Saudaramu akan baik-baik saja.

734
00:35:58,501 --> 00:36:00,134
Ini identitas barumu,

735
00:36:00,136 --> 00:36:02,970
dan juga kata sandi untuk sebuah
rekening bank dengan nominal $2.5 juta.

736
00:36:02,972 --> 00:36:04,405
Pergilah ke Cartagena, cari bar

737
00:36:04,407 --> 00:36:06,073
bernama Sol Azul di Boca Grande.

738
00:36:06,075 --> 00:36:07,641
- Carilah Ruiz.
- Siapa dia?

739
00:36:07,643 --> 00:36:10,344
Entahlah.

740
00:36:10,346 --> 00:36:12,413
Pergilah sekarang.

741
00:36:12,415 --> 00:36:15,649
Kenapa...
Kenapa kau menolongku?

742
00:36:15,651 --> 00:36:18,686
Aku cuma mengikuti perintah,

743
